The shallot-merlot sauce itself was exceptional, and was the best part of this recipe. I will make this again, but will grill the steaks (or use some other method) instead of cooking them in the skillet. I did not have a problem with getting the sauce to thicken - the key is just to turn up the heat and keep it moving. The faster it boils, the more quickly it will reduce.

