Rating: 3
Very good recipe. Bascially, I doubled it and made what I like to call "Real World" modifications to the recipe. Use a one whole shallot and to prevent the steak from getting cold while I was making the sauce. I instead seared the steak for about two minutes on each side and put it in a 350 degree oven and immeadiatly turned it down to 250 while I made the sauce. Steaks came out perfect med-rare. You could easily do a lower temp if you like it less done or visa-versa.